/addhtmlfaq moms, <button name="send" value="/j mom">Mono OM subroom</button><br><br><a href=https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/monotype-om-mega-thread.3714698/>OM Megathread</a><br><br>Click the arrow to the left of an OM to see a brief description :)<details><summary><a href=https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/monotype-om-mega-thread.3714698/post-9476495>AAA</a></summary>Almost Any Ability (AAA) Monotype is an OM where Pokemon have access to "almost any ability" with the exception of a few that the council and the community deem broken or unhealthy for this metagame.</details><details><summary><a href=https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/monotype-om-mega-thread.3714698/post-9476494>CAP</a></summary>Monotype CAP is a Monotype OM which includes CAP (community made <b>C</b>reate-<b>A</b>-<b>P</b>okemon) Pokemon.</details><details><summary><a href=https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/monotype-om-mega-thread.3714698/post-9476493>LC</a></summary>LC Monotype is a fun and unique metagame where you get to use baby Pokemon! Little Cup is a format where everyone Pokemon on your team needs to be the first evolution in their line, and they'll be battling at level 5.</details><details><summary><a href=https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/sv-monothreat-format-resources.3730755/>Monothreat</a></summary>Monothreat is a Monotype OM whereby all teams are the same type, this type will be announced beforehand to give you time to build teams with tactics in mind to counter their own typing.</details><details><summary><a href=https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/monotype-om-mega-thread.3714698/post-9476491>STAB</a></summary>STABmons Monotype is a unique metagame where Pokemon may learn nearly any move that is the same type as them.</details><details><summary><a href=https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/monotype-om-mega-thread.3714698/post-9476492>Terastal</a></summary>Terastal Monotype is an OM where Pokemon can Terastallize to <b>any type</b>, as Terastal Clause is removed from this format.</details><details><summary><a href="https://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/sv-national-dex-monotype-sample-teams.3716842/">National Dex</a></summary>National Dex Monotype (NDM) is a tier where you can use nearly all Pokemon that have ever been released, as well as Mega stones & Z-crystals.</details>
